Boron Trifluoride neutron detector

x4freetext: 4pi flat-response graphite-sphere detector.
Corrected for:
. neutron yields from other isotopes of the target
element,
. other elements in the target compound,
. target contaminants; the only serious target
contaminant was the presence of 37Cl in the Pt
backing which was corrected for using Pt blank.
. backgrounds from the target backing and from the
accelerator; the main contaminant was 37Cl in
platinum backing which were measured using a
platinum blank.
No information on uncertainties.
